OL,3,GSouth West
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FA rather grey start in places
OL,6,Fbut cloud will lift and break allowing
OL,7,Fsome good spells of sunshine to
OL,8,Fdevelop. A few showers also possible,
OL,9,Fespecially towards the west of the
OL,10,Fregion. Feeling fresher than of late.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTonight:FA largely dry evening with
OL,13,Fsome late spells of sunshine,
OL,14,Fespecially in the east. Overnight
OL,15,Fremaining dry although cloud
OL,16,Fincreasing and the breeze freshening
OL,17,Fin the west towards dawn.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
