OL,3,GSouth West
OL,4,
OL,5,CMonday:FA bright start, but cloud will
OL,6,Fcontinue to build from the west. Rain
OL,7,Fwill reach western coasts by mid-
OL,8,Fmorning before gradually spreading
OL,9,Feastwards throughout the rest of the
OL,10,Fday.
OL,11,
OL,12,COutlook for Tuesday to Thursday:FRather
OL,13,Fchangeable throughout the period with
OL,14,Fa mix of sunshine and showers
OL,15,Finterspersed with a longer spell of
OL,16,Frain on Wednesday. Temperatures near
OL,17,Faverage for early June.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
